Itu kotor!

14:18.542 --> 14:19.959
Aduh!

14:22.709 --> 14:23.459
A--Apa?

14:23.584 --> 14:24.209
Astaga,

14:24.375 --> 14:26.292
Nishimiya-san, kamu baik-baik saja?

14:26.792 --> 14:28.876
