01:06:29.501 --> 01:06:30.501
Apa?

01:06:31.250 --> 01:06:32.375
Tentang ini?

01:06:34.209 --> 01:06:36.209
Aku...ige...moo...

01:06:42.209 --> 01:06:43.042
Hah?...

01:06:46.876 --> 01:06:49.167
Aku mau!

01:06:58.292 --> 01:06:59.626
Bulan?

01:07:00.417 --> 01:07:01.417
Setuju.

